§ SUBDOMAIN-LAYOUT (already-spec/21 amended)
  ⊑ downloads.apocky.com           ← binary-delivery CDN · per-project paths · /labyrinth/v1.0.0.zip · /cssl/csslc-v0.1.0.zip
  ⊑ api.apocky.com                 ← cssl-edge serverless-functions · /api/labyrinth/* · /api/cssl/* · /api/auth/*
  ⊑ akashic.apocky.com             ← cross-project Akashic-Records browser (per spec/18)
  ⊑ mycelium.apocky.com            ← cross-project mycelium status + opt-in management
